That's the stupidest thing I have ever heard.

475
00:30:24,240 --> 00:30:26,290
你想就这样坐等奥德伍夫攻破城门么
You'd rather wait until Aldwulf is upon the gates?

476
00:30:26,430 --> 00:30:30,400
