You and your duty--

478
00:30:32,850 --> 00:30:33,870
要服从国王
to the king,

479
00:30:34,010 --> 00:30:35,350
要善待妻子
to your wife,

480
00:30:35,620 --> 00:30:37,010
还要敬奉上帝
to God.

481
00:30:38,360 --> 00:30:39,990
