Why are you so keen to go out there?

484
00:30:44,010 --> 00:30:45,300
这无异于自投罗网
It's a suicide mission.

485
00:30:45,550 --> 00:30:47,220
自投罗网
Suicide?

486
00:30:48,570 --> 00:30:51,530
