Like your Scriptures--

498
00:31:27,360 --> 00:31:29,190
字太多
too many words.

499
00:31:33,950 --> 00:31:36,130
回去
Go back inside.

500
00:31:40,460 --> 00:31:42,400
你知道你赢不了我
You know you can't beat me.

501
00:31:44,630 --> 00:31:46,320
