我们在这里集结
We are banded together here.

517
00:32:57,480 --> 00:32:59,740
团结成一个整体  没人例外
We stand as one. No exceptions.

518
00:33:00,000 --> 00:33:01,640
没人例外
No exceptions.

519
00:33:02,470 --> 00:33:05,870
现在各就各位  保持警惕
Now man the battlements, and keep watch.

520
00:33:06,330 --> 00:33:08,030
