563
00:35:50,080 --> 00:35:52,660
上帝给我了我所愿的一切
God has given me all I could want.

564
00:35:52,810 --> 00:35:54,820
他也可以轻易收回
He could take it from me just as easily.

565
00:35:54,970 --> 00:35:59,250
他为何要收回  你是如此虔诚
Why would he? You are so devoted.

566
00:35:59,550 --> 00:36:01,870
如果那虔诚受到了考验呢
What if that devotion were tested?

567
00:36:02,250 --> 00:36:04,940
如果明天我就要失去朋友和爱人呢
If tomorrow saw me losing friends and loved ones?

568
00:36:05,060 --> 00:36:09,410
那不是虔诚信仰的定义吗
Is that not the definition of true faith?

569
00:36:09,540 --> 00:36:12,570
你害怕会失去什么吗
You fear that something will be taken from you?

570
00:36:12,710 --> 00:36:13,760
我半夜醒来  感觉冰冷
I wake at night, cold,

571
00:36:13,910 --> 00:36:16,840
害怕会失去桂妮维尔
fearing that Guinevere will be taken from me.

572
00:36:16,970 --> 00:36:19,370
这是对我罪孽的惩罚
Retribution for my sins.

573
00:36:26,140 --> 00:36:29,690
我担忧的不是你对上帝的信仰
It's not your faith in God I'd worry about,

574
00:36:30,240 --> 00:36:32,680
而是你错信他人
but your faith in man.

575
00:36:39,790 --> 00:36:43,720
听着  你有护卫
Listen to me. You have champions--

576
00:36:43,870 --> 00:36:45,650
凯  里昂提斯
Kay, Leontes.

577
00:36:45,820 --> 00:36:47,210
你无须孤军奋战
You do not have to do this alone.

578
00:36:47,220 --> 00:36:48,610
我不能躲在他们身后
I cannot hide behind them.

579
00:36:48,740 --> 00:36:52,560
让他们照顾你并非躲避
It isn't hiding to let them care for you.

580
00:36:52,710 --> 00:36:54,350
而是爱护
To love you.

581
00:36:55,890 --> 00:36:58,240
我花了很长时间才找到你
It's taken me so long to find you,

582
00:36:59,140 --> 00:37:01,050
我现在不能失去你
I can't bear the thought of losing you now.

583
00:37:01,180 --> 00:37:03,990
你无需证明你对我的爱
You do not need to prove your love to me.

584
00:37:04,620 --> 00:37:06,060
我知道的
I know it.

585
00:37:06,210 --> 00:37:07,970
我也爱你
And I return it.

586
00:37:13,260 --> 00:37:16,660
你不仅是我母亲  更是卡米洛特的母亲
You're not just a mother to me, but to all of Camelot.

587
00:37:20,630 --> 00:37:23,790
亚瑟  你要去哪里
Arthur, where are you going?

588
00:37:24,400 --> 00:37:27,020
今晚要把一切说清楚
Tonight is not a night to leave things unsaid.

589
00:37:54,460 --> 00:37:57,190
知道吗  我刚才真想杀了你
You know I wanted to kill you back there?

590
00:37:58,610 --> 00:38:00,320
我发现了
I noticed.

591
00:38:02,400 --> 00:38:04,280
你身手不错
You fought well.

592
00:38:05,450 --> 00:38:06,740
我无法打败你
I couldn't beat you.

593
00:38:06,850 --> 00:38:08,740
这是好事  真的
It's a good thing, really.

594
00:38:10,090 --> 00:38:12,140
我以前战无不胜
I always could before.

595
00:38:14,450 --> 00:38:17,220
这是信仰给你的力量吗
Is that what faith gives you?

596
00:38:18,010 --> 00:38:20,720
我长年浴血奋战
I spent years bathed in blood.

597
00:38:20,870 --> 00:38:23,780
男人之战  感觉是种荣誉
Man versus man. It felt like it had honour.

598
00:38:24,650 --> 00:38:26,710
直到有一天的战事中
Then one day we rode into battle.

599
00:38:29,090 --> 00:38:31,710
我们黎明时分进入一个村庄  战事激烈
We entered a village at dawn; the fighting was fierce,

600
00:38:31,850 --> 00:38:33,980
我对付一个战士
and I took arms against a warrior.

601
00:38:34,110 --> 00:38:35,320
正当我把他击倒在地时
Just as I flung him to the ground,

602
00:38:35,450 --> 00:38:37,450
另一个人跳上了我的背
another jumped on my back. I...

603
00:38:38,180 --> 00:38:41,520
我毫不犹豫把他扔在地上
I didn't even think. I just threw him to the floor

604
00:38:41,630 --> 00:38:43,560
一剑刺中了他
and I drove my sword through him.

605
00:38:50,420 --> 00:38:53,410
但这战士不是成人  只是个小孩
Except the warrior wasn't a man; it was a boy,

606
00:38:53,660 --> 00:38:55,550
不足12岁
no more than 12.

607
00:38:55,710 --> 00:38:58,340
他甚至还拿不起剑
He could barely lift the sword that he held.

608
00:39:00,750 --> 00:39:07,050
我看见他母亲对儿子之死伤心欲绝
And I watched his mother, all that pain and grief for her son.

609
00:39:12,250 --> 00:39:14,300
那晚还是如常举行庆功宴
That night we feasted to our victory as usual,

610
00:39:14,420 --> 00:39:16,460
但我毫无感觉
and I felt nothing.

611
00:39:22,970 --> 00:39:25,610
那天午夜后  我
Later on in the middle of the night I...

612
00:39:26,720 --> 00:39:28,400
我祈祷了
I prayed.

613
00:39:29,830 --> 00:39:31,750
我祈求上帝原谅我
I asked God to forgive me.

614
00:39:36,440 --> 00:39:37,910
他原谅你了吗
Did he?

615
00:39:56,160 --> 00:39:59,010
-能跟你聊聊吗  -你不该来这里
- Can I speak to you? - You shouldn't be in here.

616
00:39:59,160 --> 00:40:01,980
我要说的话不能被外人知晓
What I need to say cannot be said in public.

617
00:40:03,040 --> 00:40:05,960
那你就该绝口不提
Then you shouldn't be saying it to me at all.

618
00:40:06,460 --> 00:40:08,410
我们之间的...
How it was...

619
00:40:09,470 --> 00:40:12,720
感觉  我以前从没意识到
...between us. I've never known that before.

620
00:40:13,370 --> 00:40:15,390
从没有过那样的感觉
Never felt like that.

621
00:40:15,830 --> 00:40:16,450
够了
Stop.

622
00:40:16,600 --> 00:40:17,930
请让我说完
Please!

623
00:40:21,820 --> 00:40:24,530
我对明日之战没有把握
I don't know if we can prevail tomorrow.

624
00:40:25,870 --> 00:40:27,470
亚瑟
Arthur.

625
00:40:28,490 --> 00:40:30,340
明天也许会成为我们生命的终结点
Tomorrow could be the end of all of us,

626
00:40:30,470 --> 00:40:33,390
我不想带着满腹心事死去
and I don't want to die without having said this.

627
00:40:36,670 --> 00:40:38,760
里昂提斯是我的护卫
Leontes is my champion.

628
00:40:41,120 --> 00:40:43,540
我尊敬他  我永远不会
I honour him, and would never do anything

629
00:40:43,670 --> 00:40:45,420
做出破坏你们婚姻的事
to break your marriage.

630
00:40:47,790 --> 00:40:49,800
但我要你知道
But I need you to know...

631
00:40:54,180 --> 00:40:55,660
我爱你
...I love you.

632
00:41:06,830 --> 00:41:08,320
你走吧
Go.

633
00:41:08,450 --> 00:41:10,510
求你
Please.

634
00:41:25,940 --> 00:41:29,290
奥德伍夫  你个狗杂种
Ardulf, you bog-dwelling inbred!

635
00:41:29,420 --> 00:41:31,390
等你跟你姐姐交媾完
When you're finished interfering with your sister,

636
00:41:31,540 --> 00:41:34,100
来挑战彭德拉根的男人们试试吧
come and have a go at the men of Pendragon!

637
00:41:34,250 --> 00:41:36,410
-懦夫  -很久以前
- Cowards!  - Long long ago in this...

638
00:41:36,550 --> 00:41:39,280
-奥德伍夫  -在这古老的土地上
- Ardulf!  - ...ancient land

639
00:41:39,430 --> 00:41:44,370
两山之间  战事突发
A battle took place where 2 hills now stand

640
00:41:44,500 --> 00:41:46,950
尸横遍野
And on the plain

641
00:41:47,520 --> 00:41:51,160
血流成河
There lay the slain

642
00:41:51,290 --> 00:41:56,400
生灵涂炭  胜者尤败
For neither the battle was won

643
00:42:01,810 --> 00:42:06,200
里昂提斯爱桂妮维尔胜过爱生命
Leontes loves Guinevere more than life itself.

644
00:42:06,340 --> 00:42:10,240
她是他的全部未来
She is the future he pins all his hopes upon.

645
00:42:10,380 --> 00:42:13,680
卡米洛特的希望则寄托在了亚瑟身上
And Camelot's hopes rest on Arthur's honour.

646
00:42:13,820 --> 00:42:16,440
亚瑟和他护卫间的隔阂
A wedge between Arthur and his champion

647
00:42:16,590 --> 00:42:18,360
能毁掉一切
could bring it all down.

648
00:42:18,500 --> 00:42:23,850
他们都对伊格兰夫人信任有加
And they all confide in the Lady Igraine.

649
00:42:41,120 --> 00:42:43,600
万事已备
I have what I need.

650
00:42:43,790 --> 00:42:46,430
你确定你想这么做吗
Are you sure this is what you want?

651
00:42:48,790 --> 00:42:51,850
你说过我被赐予这能力是有原因的
You said I'd been given the gift for a reason.

652
00:42:53,740 --> 00:42:57,150
现在我知道原因何在了
Now I know what it is.

653
00:43:13,840 --> 00:43:18,600
-骑士  -有骑士过来了
- Riders! - Riders approaching!

654
00:43:18,740 --> 00:43:20,730
他们回来了
The men return!

655
00:43:26,360 --> 00:43:28,080
发生了何事
What happened?

656
00:43:28,460 --> 00:43:30,520
其他人呢
Where are the others?

657
00:43:32,440 --> 00:43:33,550
死了
Dead.

658
00:43:33,700 --> 00:43:35,240
只剩了我们几个
We are all that remain.

659
00:43:35,380 --> 00:43:37,310
我说了这是胡来
I told you this was madness!

660
00:43:37,710 --> 00:43:39,550
敌军情况如何  离你们还有多远
And what of the enemy, how far behind you?

661
00:43:39,700 --> 00:43:40,530
他们走了
They are gone.

662
00:43:40,690 --> 00:43:43,190
-去哪了  巴尔东吗  -听他说完
- Gone where? To Bardon Pass? - Let him speak.

663
00:43:43,320 --> 00:43:46,430
他们走了  我们战胜了他们
They're gone. We defeated them.

664
00:43:46,590 --> 00:43:47,460
什么
You did what?

665
00:43:47,610 --> 00:43:49,280
我们突袭了他们
We took them by surprise.

666
00:43:49,430 --> 00:43:50,970
战斗很惨烈
The fighting was vicious.

667
00:43:51,120 --> 00:43:52,550
其他战士们呢
Where are the rest of your comrades?

668
00:43:52,700 --> 00:43:55,150
在战斗中牺牲了
Fallen on the battlefield.

669
00:43:55,300 --> 00:43:56,710
全部吗
All of them?

670
00:43:57,760 --> 00:44:01,260
奥德伍夫死了吗  可否见到他的尸体
Is Aldwulf dead? Did you claim his body?

671
00:44:01,390 --> 00:44:03,030
有几个人逃走了
The last few fled.

672
00:44:03,210 --> 00:44:05,610
我们无力再追了
We had no men left to follow.

673
00:44:06,290 --> 00:44:07,960
你们做得很好
You have done well.

674
00:44:08,490 --> 00:44:10,850
你们做出了巨大的牺牲
The sacrifice you have made is huge.

675
00:44:11,020 --> 00:44:14,700
我的人以为彭德拉根而战为豪
My men are proud to fight under the Pendragon banner.

676
00:44:15,070 --> 00:44:16,460
姐姐
Sister.

677
00:44:17,640 --> 00:44:19,260
我们都欠你的情
We are in your debt.

678
00:44:19,400 --> 00:44:21,630
但你的人元气大伤  希望你能
But with your men so weakened, maybe you should accompany us

679
00:44:21,780 --> 00:44:23,560
跟我们一起回卡米洛特
back to Camelot.

680
00:44:26,280 --> 00:44:28,730
我们还要为勇士们准备葬礼
We have brave men to bury.

681
00:44:30,310 --> 00:44:32,480
我的根在这里
My place is here.

682
00:44:32,620 --> 00:44:34,470
-太可笑了  -你是说你很遗憾
- What a tease. - So what you're saying is

683
00:44:34,630 --> 00:44:36,450
我们没去参加那必死无疑的战斗
you're disappointed we didn't face certain death?

684
00:44:36,570 --> 00:44:38,970
我是说  我很遗憾自己完全错过了那战斗
What I'm saying is, I'm sad I missed the fight completely.

685
00:44:39,110 --> 00:44:41,390
摩根的人取得了一场辉煌的胜利
Morgan's men have claimed a famous victory.

686
00:44:41,700 --> 00:44:43,620
她的传奇有又新料了
Her legend grows.

687
00:44:43,760 --> 00:44:45,310
你怀疑她
You doubt her?

688
00:44:47,210 --> 00:44:49,650
没有他不怀疑的人  他就这样
He doubts everyone. It's his way.

689
00:44:50,840 --> 00:44:54,550
总是一副高深莫测的样子
Keep up the whole inscrutable man of magic thing.

690
00:44:54,800 --> 00:44:57,760
我只是觉得死要见尸
I just want to see the dead bodies.

691
00:45:04,130 --> 00:45:07,380
我们熬过了这个夜晚  我很欣慰
I'm relieved we all made it out of this night.

692
00:45:07,580 --> 00:45:08,960
是的
Yes.

693
00:45:09,530 --> 00:45:11,800
他们都等着呢  不如...
Uh, they're all waiting, so...

694
00:45:12,140 --> 00:45:14,200
你究竟有何魔力
What is it about you?

695
00:45:14,400 --> 00:45:17,690
你这张脸为何能让男人们甘愿沉沦
What is it about that face that makes men weak?

696
00:45:25,400 --> 00:45:26,420
准备好了吗
Are we ready?

697
00:45:26,550 --> 00:45:29,470
好了  我只是...
Yes. I just wanted...

698
00:45:29,600 --> 00:45:32,080
想再看这地方最后一眼
...one last look at the place.

699
00:45:32,880 --> 00:45:34,370
你怀念这里
You miss it?

700
00:45:34,980 --> 00:45:36,580
不
No.

701
00:45:36,770 --> 00:45:38,860
我已经有新家了
I've got a new home now.

702
00:45:39,470 --> 00:45:41,400
卡米洛特
Camelot.

703
00:45:53,060 --> 00:45:54,300
有何指示
What are the orders?

704
00:45:54,450 --> 00:45:56,250
去召集一些人
You are to recruit some men--

705
00:45:56,390 --> 00:45:57,860
不是我们的人
not ours--

706
00:45:57,870 --> 00:46:00,260
要找其他对亚瑟心怀不满的人
others disaffected with Arthur.

707
00:46:00,590 --> 00:46:04,330
去袭击巴尔东的边区村落
You will attack the outpost at Bardon Pass.

708
00:46:04,480 --> 00:46:06,490
这能把国王引过去
This will draw out the king.

709
00:46:07,300 --> 00:46:09,800
别给他留机会
Offer him no quarter.

710
00:46:10,930 --> 00:46:13,300
我要摩根亲自对我下令
I want to hear that from Morgan herself.

711
00:46:13,450 --> 00:46:15,630
我已经把命令传达给你了
You're hearing it from me.

712
00:46:16,210 --> 00:46:19,530
需要我告诉她你拒绝了吗
Or shall I tell her that you refuse?

713
00:46:20,320 --> 00:46:21,980
我会做的
I'll do it.

714
00:46:34,760 --> 00:46:36,760
你没事吧
Are you all right?

715
00:46:36,930 --> 00:46:39,470
没事  只是有点累
Fine. Just weary.

716
00:46:39,630 --> 00:46:41,250
昨晚是个漫长之夜
It was a long night.

717
00:47:00,120 --> 00:47:02,170
修女
Oh, Sister.

718
00:47:02,320 --> 00:47:04,430
我知道这都是摩根的命令
I know that this is Morgan's bidding.

719
00:47:04,570 --> 00:47:09,060
放我走  我保证你不会受到责罚
Let me go and I will make sure that you are not punished.

720
00:47:11,610 --> 00:47:13,370
你真以为
Do you really think

721
00:47:13,480 --> 00:47:16,350
国王不会在意我去了哪吗
that the king will not wonder where I am?

722
00:47:16,490 --> 00:47:18,360
他不会发现的
I know he won't.

723
00:47:28,700 --> 00:47:30,520
回家真好
It's good to be home.

724
00:47:31,960 --> 00:47:33,610
是啊
Yes.

725
00:47:39,330 --> 00:47:41,230
真好
It is.
